{
  "stem": "3964.5",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 119,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] we were still outside at this assembly.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 120,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And after a while, they told us that we could go back in the barracks and get whatever our personal things were we had, which was nothing, you know, and report again in 5 minutes or 10 minutes, whatever it was, at the assembly.",
      "word_count": 48
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 121,
      "text": "They had all our names, so you had to comply.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 122,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Didn't have to comply, but the consequences of not complying was death.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 123,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I said goodbye to my father.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 124,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And he wanted me to stay with him.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 125,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And I wanted to and I didn't want to.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 126,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] It was really a difficult choice for me to make, to leave him there.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 127,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] My dad said to me, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] stay with me, [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] stay with me.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 128,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I said, Papa, I can't.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 129,
      "text": "I have to go.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 130,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 7 SECONDS] And I went, said goodbye to him.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 131,
      "text": "Obviously, that's the last I saw of my father.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 132,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] I don't know what happened to the women in-- I guess the same thing happened to the women, what happened to us.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 133,
      "text": "They put us into marching groups [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] shortly thereafter, after we got back to the assembly.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 134,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] and we marched from [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Stutthof back to Danzig.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 135,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] We stayed overnight in a holding camp.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 136,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] It was called Rehagen.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 137,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] What a terrible, terrible place.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
